On Monday, August 2, 1999,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        SCHLOSSER ALT by 
                        Brauerei Schlosser GmbH, Eingang Ratinger Mauer 40213 Dusseldorf.
                        The USPTO has given the SCHLOSSER ALT 
                        trademark serial  number of  75765862.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for SCHLOSSER ALT is 
                        
                        
                                            MARK B. HARISON of 
                                            VENABLE LLP,  P.O. BOX 34385, WASHINGTON, DC 20045-9998 
                                .
                            The SCHLOSSER ALT trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Light Beverage Products 
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for SCHLOSSER ALT 
                            is beers. 
                            





