This is a brand page for the SCHLOSSER trademark by Companhia Industrial Schlosser S/A 
                                in Brusque, Santa Catarina, , .
Write a review about a product or service associated with this SCHLOSSER trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Companhia Industrial Schlosser S/A of the SCHLOSSER trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the SCHLOSSER trademark.
                           






On Wednesday, September 22, 1982,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        SCHLOSSER by 
                        Companhia Industrial Schlosser S/A, Brusque, Santa Catarina.
                        The USPTO has given the SCHLOSSER 
                        trademark serial  number of  73387646.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is CONTINUED USE NOT FILED WITHIN GRACE PERIOD, UN-REVIVABLE.
                        The correspondent listed for SCHLOSSER is 
                        
                        
                                            D. Paul Weaver of 
                                            Suite 1104,  2001 Jefferson Davis Hwy., Arlington VA   22202 
                                .
                            The SCHLOSSER trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Fabrics
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for SCHLOSSER 
                            is Cotton Towels, Cotton Tablecloths and Cotton Fabrics in the Piece. 
                            





